---
title: Peppercorn Steak with Crispy Roasted Potatoes and Creamed Kale
description: Creamy peppercorn sauce over juicy steak is date night perfection. It’s impossible to mess up, yet bound to impress! Classic roasted potatoes and greens complete the ultimate Valentine’s Day dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5693ee5dfd2cb9a8688b4567.jpg
